<paragraph base="F32570073" principles="yes" id="IFRS09_5.4.4"><paranum>5.4.4</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 9"/><data name="paranum" value="5.4.4"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS09_P0310">An entity shall directly reduce the <xref base="F32570695" href="IFRS09_APPA.dita#IFRS09_APPA/IFRS09_P0713">gross carrying amount of a financial asset<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0155"/></ph></xref> when the entity has no reasonable expectations of recovering a financial asset in its entirety or a portion thereof. A write-off constitutes a <xref base="F32570634" href="IFRS09_APPA.dita#IFRS09_APPA/IFRS09_P0687">derecognition<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0085"/></ph></xref> event (see <xref base="F41732469" href="IFRS09_gB3.2.16-B3.2.17.dita#IFRS09_gB3.2.16-B3.2.17/IFRS09_gB3.2.16-B3.2.17_TI" id="IFRS09_X0454">paragraph B3.2.16(r)</xref>).</p></body></paragraph>